Package apoc.generate.config

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GeneratorConfiguration
    A configuration of a GraphGenerator.
    RelationshipGeneratorConfig
    Configuration for a RelationshipGenerator.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BarabasiAlbertConfig
    RelationshipGeneratorConfig for BarabasiAlbertRelationshipGenerator.
    BasicGeneratorConfig
    Basic implementation of GeneratorConfiguration where everything can be configured by constructor instantiation, except for batch size, which defaults to 1000.
    DistributionBasedConfig
    SimpleDegreeDistribution serving as a RelationshipGeneratorConfig.
    ErdosRenyiConfig
    RelationshipGeneratorConfig for ErdosRenyiRelationshipGenerator.
    NumberOfNodesBasedConfig
    RelationshipGeneratorConfig that is based on an explicitly defined number of nodes in the network.
    WattsStrogatzConfig
    RelationshipGeneratorConfig for WattsStrogatzRelationshipGenerator.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidConfigException
    Exception signifying an invalid config used for graph generation.
